quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  26,53,Fir’awnis magaalota keessatti walitti qabdoota ergee
  26,54,“Dhugumatti warri kun gareewwan xiqqoodha
  26,55,Isaanis dhugumatti nu dallansiisoodha
  26,56,"Nutis baay’ee of eegdota” [jedhe]"
  26,57,Ashaakiltiileefi burqaawwan irraas isaan baafne
  26,58,Kuusaa qabeenyaafi iddoowwan kabajamaa irraas
  26,59,Akka kanatti Ilmaan Israa’iil ishee dhaalchifne
  26,60,Bariifatoo ta’anii isaan hordofan
  26,61,"Yeroma gareen lamaan wal argan, gareen Muusaa “nuti dhugumatti [garee Fir’awniin] dhaqqabamoodha” jedhan"
  26,62,"[Muusaan] ni jedhe: “lakkisaa! Dhugumatti, Gooftaan kiyya na wajjin jiraInni [furmaatatti] na qajeelcha.”"
  26,63,"Gara Muusaatti “ulee keetiin galaana rukuti” jechuun wahyii goone[Yeroma inni dhahu] qoqqoodamee Kutaan qoodama isaa hunduu akka gaara guddaa ta’e"
  26,64,Bakka sanattis warra biraa dhiheessine
  26,65,Muusaafi warra isa waliin turan hundaa ni baraarsine
  26,66,Sana booda warra biroo bishaaniin dhidhimsine
  26,67,"Dhugumatti, kana keessa mallattootu jiraIrra hedduun isaanii Mu’uminoota hin taane"
  26,68,"Dhugumatti Rabbiin kee, Isumatu injifataa, rahmata godhaadha"
  26,69,Seenaa Ibraahimis isaan irratti dubbisi